title: AFC East Breakdown + Late Round Dart Throws - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/21
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a 2022 season preview for the Bills, Patriots, Dolphins, and Jets! Can Tua Tagovailoa and Zach Wilson take a step forward? Will Josh Allen repeat as the top fantasy QB for a third consecutive season? Which Pats RB to draft? Plus, a number of players to target late in drafts during Best Ball Breakdown, presented by Underdog Fantasy! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 21st, 2022.

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
